{"lemma":"جُوعُ","slug":"جُوعُ","root":"ج.#.ع","root_slug":"ج-_-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-_-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جُوع","root":"جوع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":4},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n6715"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8F%D9%88%D8%B9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hunger"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"starvation"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَاعَ (jāʕa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to starve"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/d͡ʒuːʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6715","headword_ar":"جُوعٌ","root":"jwE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", a subst., (Msb, TA,) signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hunger;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"emptiness of the belly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ibaEN","text_ar":"شِبَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majaAEapN","text_ar":"مَجَاعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [properly an inf. n.,] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majowaEapN","text_ar":"مَجْوَعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majuwEapN","text_ar":"مَجُوعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juwEFA lahu wanuwEFA","text_ar":"جُوعًا لَهُ وَنُوعًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[May God decree"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hunger to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: accord. to Sb, an instance of inf. ns. in the accus. case by reason of a verb understood: it is a form of imprecation: and the latter noun may not be put before the former, because it is a corroborative to it: (TA:) or, accord. to some,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuwEN","text_ar":"نُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means “ thirst. ” (S, &c., in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nwE","text_ar":"نوع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmu majaAEapK","text_ar":"عَامُ مَجَاعَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majowaEapK","text_ar":"مَجْوَعَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majuwEapK","text_ar":"مَجُوعَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A year in which is hunger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"emptiness of the belly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmu AlmajaAEapi","text_ar":"عَامُ المَجَاعَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmajuwEapi","text_ar":"المَجُوعَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the year of hunger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: (Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majaAy^iEu","text_ar":"مَجَايِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majaAwihu","text_ar":"مَجَاوِهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": as in the phrases"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSaAbatohumu AlmajaAwiEu","text_ar":"اَصَابَتْهُمُ المَجَاوِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cases of hunger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"befell them"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqaEuwAfiY","text_ar":"وَقَعُوافِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmajaAwiEi","text_ar":"المَجَاوِعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They fell into cases of hunger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~aDaAEapu mina AlmajaAEapi","text_ar":"الرَّضَاعَةُ مِنَ المَجَاعَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sucking which occasions interdiction"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of marriage with the woman whose milk is sucked and certain of her relations]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is that consequent upon hunger"},{"kind":"text","text":"which is stopped by the milk in the time of infancy of the child; not when the child's hunger is only to be stopped by solid food. (Mgh.) [See also 1 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rDE","text_ar":"رضع"},{"kind":"text","text":".] And it is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samanu","text_ar":"سَمَنُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalobK bijuwEi A^aholihi","text_ar":"كَلْبٍ بِجُوعِ اَهْلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The dog's becoming fat is"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the hunger of his owners"},{"kind":"text","text":"occasioned by] murrain befalling the camels; (K, * TA;) his owners falling into hunger and distress and leanness: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"klb","text_ar":"كلب"},{"kind":"text","text":"was the name of a certain man, who was an object of fear, wherefore he was asked for a pledge, and he pledged his family: then obtaining possession of the camels, or cattle, of the people to whom he had pledged his family, he drove them away, and left his family: (K, TA:) some relate this prov. differently, saying ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samina kalobN","text_ar":"سَمِنَ كَلْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"“ a dog, ” or “ Kelb, ” “ became fat, ” and]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bibuw^osi A^aholihi","text_ar":"بِبُوْسِ اَهْلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[“ by reason of the distress of his owners, ” or “ his family ”]. (TA.) [See Freytag's Arab. Prov. i. 615.]"}],"source_refs":["Msb","TA","K","S"]}]}}